text: Gustavo Ramírez (born 15 May 1941) is a Guatemalan wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Guatemalan male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Guatemala Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from San Marcos Department
